messages.messageBody:
In the "Naked Portrait Laid Bare at Compton Verney", there is this
quote that I liked.

"It may not be easy to look at so many naked portraits, but they
certainly are revealing."

messages.subject: a 24 hour museum (online fun)
messages.msgSnippet: I was looking for art for a background of a page, and came upon this site.  You might think you re not much interested in England, but you ll find something
messages.messageBody:
I was looking for art for a background of a page, and came upon this
site. You might think you're not much interested in England, but
you'll find something fun. Just in the few moments I played with it,
I looked at Flemish paintings I hadn't seen and section on "2000
years of art and sex" (article on an exhibit at the Bubicon), and
there' something about seaside resorts which Jane Austen fans might
need to read, and some history of Punk art and.... Well there it is:

http://www.24hourmuseum.org.uk/
The National Virtual Museum, Celebrating UK Culture


ï¿¼



It's history and art and geography and archeology and politics/
finance and there's a link called "Trails"--check that out!

Sandra
